summary: Newer version on system (broken)
description: |
  System repo: foo-1.4-bad
  Pre-installed: foo-1.0
  Artifacts: None

  The broken update does not affect because `foo` is pre-installed
  and we do not upgrade it.

environment+:
  SYSTEM_PACKAGE: foo-1.4-bad
  EXPECTED_PACKAGE: foo-1.0
  PRE_INSTALLED_PACKAGE: rpms/foo-1.0/foo-1.0*.rpm

/only-foo:
  summary+: " (only foo requested)"

/with-bar:
  summary+: " (foo and bar requested)"
  context+:
    with_bar: "true"
  environment+:
    SYSTEM_PACKAGE+: " bar"
